<P class=MsoNormal 0in 0pt **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0.25in?><FONT size=2><FONT color=#ff0000><SPAN **Zowie**?COLOR: Verdana? FONT-FAMILY: red;>This is something that will be considered in future expansions</SPAN><SPAN **Zowie**?FONT-FAMILY: Verdana?></SPAN></FONT></FONT></P>
<OL type=1 start=8 **Zowie**?MARGIN-TOP: 0in?>
<LI class=MsoNormal 0in .5in? list tab-stops: lfo1; level1 l0 mso-list: **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0pt;><SPAN **Zowie**?FONT-FAMILY: Verdana?>Improved pet heals<FONT size=2><FONT color=#000000></FONT></FONT></SPAN></LI></OL>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in 0pt **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0.25in?><SPAN **Zowie**?COLOR: Verdana? FONT-FAMILY: red;><FONT size=2><FONT color=#ff0000>Currently being evaluated</FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<OL type=1 start=9 **Zowie**?MARGIN-TOP: 0in?>
<LI class=MsoNormal 0in .5in? list tab-stops: lfo1; level1 l0 mso-list: **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0pt;><SPAN **Zowie**?FONT-FAMILY: Verdana?>Allow Hobble of spirits, to stack with ALL <FONT size=2><FONT color=#000000>pet proc buffs</FONT></FONT></SPAN></LI></OL>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in 0pt **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0.25in?><SPAN **Zowie**?COLOR: Verdana? FONT-FAMILY: red;><FONT size=2><FONT color=#ff0000>Currently being evaluated</FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<OL type=1 start=10 **Zowie**?MARGIN-TOP: 0in?>
<LI class=MsoNormal 0in .5in? list tab-stops: lfo1; level1 l0 mso-list: **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0pt;><SPAN **Zowie**?FONT-FAMILY: Verdana?>Allow the Feral swipe AA to work in PvP and it doesn’t <FONT size=2><FONT color=#000000>offer any advantages</FONT></FONT></SPAN></LI></OL>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in 0pt **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0.25in?><SPAN **Zowie**?COLOR: Verdana? FONT-FAMILY: red;><FONT size=2><FONT color=#ff0000>Currently skill abilities do not work in PvP.<SPAN yes? **Zowie**?mso-spacerun:>&nbsp; </SPAN>This is a bug and it is currently being worked on, the development team hopes to have this fixed soon.</FONT></FONT></SPAN></P></DIV></SPAN>
								<p><div style="width: 100%; height: 120; overflow: hidden;">
								
