			>
			<DIV>
<DIV><STRONG>Details on Beastlord list #9</STRONG></DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>
<P class=MsoNormal **SMURF**?MARGIN: 0in 0pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none?><SPAN ?Century Gothic?? **SMURF**?mso-bidi-font-family:><STRONG>Bestial alignment:<namespace prefix = o ns = "http://www.lithium.com/unique/URI"></STRONG></SPAN></P>
<UL type=disc **SMURF**?MARGIN-TOP: 0in?>
<LI class=MsoNormal **SMURF**?MARGIN: 0in 0pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-list: level1 tab-stops: list .5in? lfo1; l0><SPAN ?Century Gothic?? **SMURF**?mso-bidi-font-family:>Lower the refresh time on the AA.<SPAN **SMURF**?mso-spacerun: yes?>&nbsp; </SPAN>As it stands now the recast time is 72 minutes for all 3 ranks.<SPAN **SMURF**?mso-spacerun: yes?>&nbsp; </SPAN>Having the recast time be ~30 minutes would make this AA far more useful. </SPAN>
<LI class=MsoNormal **SMURF**?MARGIN: 0in 0pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-list: level1 tab-stops: list .5in? lfo1; l0><SPAN ?Century Gothic?? **SMURF**?mso-bidi-font-family:>Lower the cost of the higher ranks of the skill or add more to them to justify the cost.<SPAN **SMURF**?mso-spacerun: yes?>&nbsp; </SPAN>Currently rank 1 at 3 AA gets you a 50% boost to melee damage and 20% chance to resist spell.<SPAN **SMURF**?mso-spacerun: yes?>&nbsp; </SPAN>For 6 more AA you gain 25% more to melee damage and for 9 more AA after that you gain an additional 25% to melee damage.<SPAN **SMURF**?mso-spacerun: yes?>&nbsp; </SPAN>The higher ranks give less, but cost a lot more currently.</SPAN> 
<LI class=MsoNormal **SMURF**?MARGIN: 0in 0pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-list: level1 tab-stops: list .5in? lfo1; l0><SPAN ?Century Gothic?? **SMURF**?mso-bidi-font-family:>Add some other damage boosting element to this AA.<SPAN **SMURF**?mso-spacerun: yes?>&nbsp; </SPAN>Beastlords suffer from a division of power that really hinders our burst DPS.<SPAN **SMURF**?mso-spacerun: yes?>&nbsp; </SPAN>Bestial alignment could help with that, but in its current form it is lacking. <SPAN **SMURF**?mso-spacerun: yes?>&nbsp;</SPAN>Although the AA boosts our melee damage it doesn't do anything to help our pet damage, our spell damage or our proc damage.<SPAN **SMURF**?mso-spacerun: yes?>&nbsp; </SPAN>Consider adding a mod to the AA that would add to our DDs well under the effects of the AA. <SPAN **SMURF**?mso-spacerun: yes?>&nbsp;</SPAN>Another suggestion would be having BA also give our warder a short duration buff that raised their damage during the period of time we were under the effects of BA.<SPAN **SMURF**?mso-spacerun: yes?>&nbsp; </SPAN>Another suggestion is to let the effects of this AA stack with our level 60 disc.</SPAN> 
<LI class=MsoNormal **SMURF**?MARGIN: 0in 0pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-list: level1 tab-stops: list .5in? lfo1; l0><SPAN ?Century Gothic?? **SMURF**?mso-bidi-font-family:>Finally, BA is bugged in that if your buff slots are full or you have another illusion on you and you click the AA it is wasted.<SPAN **SMURF**?mso-spacerun: yes?>&nbsp; </SPAN>You now have to wait 72 minutes before you can try to use it again.<SPAN **SMURF**?mso-spacerun: yes?>&nbsp; </SPAN>This isn't how the AA used to work and really needs to be changed back to not wasting the AA if it doesn't take hold.</SPAN></LI></UL>
<P class=MsoNormal **SMURF**?MARGIN: 0in 0pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none?><SPAN ?Century Gothic?? **SMURF**?mso-bidi-font-family:>&nbsp;</SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal **SMURF**?MARGIN: 0in 0pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none?><SPAN ?Century Gothic?? **SMURF**?mso-bidi-font-family:><STRONG>Critical affliction:</STRONG></SPAN></P>
<UL type=disc **SMURF**?MARGIN-TOP: 0in?>
<LI class=MsoNormal **SMURF**?MARGIN: 0in 0pt; mso-layout-grid-align: l1 lfo2; none; mso-list: level1 tab-stops: list .5in?><SPAN ?Century Gothic?? **SMURF**?mso-bidi-font-family:>Remove the extra agro associated with dot crits.<SPAN **SMURF**?mso-spacerun: yes?>&nbsp; </SPAN>Dots already have enough issues as it is and having this AA generate extra agro for the extra damage it does just creates more.</SPAN> 
<LI class=MsoNormal **SMURF**?MARGIN: 0in 0pt; mso-layout-grid-align: l1 lfo2; none; mso-list: level1 tab-stops: list .5in?><SPAN ?Century Gothic?? **SMURF**?mso-bidi-font-family:>Lower the cost on the AA.<SPAN **SMURF**?mso-spacerun: yes?>&nbsp; </SPAN>Currently it costs 30AA for all 3 ranks. </SPAN></LI></UL>
<P class=MsoNormal **SMURF**?MARGIN: 0in 0pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none?><SPAN ?Century Gothic?? **SMURF**?mso-bidi-font-family:>&nbsp;</SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal **SMURF**?MARGIN: 0in 0pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none?><SPAN ?Century Gothic?? **SMURF**?mso-bidi-font-family:><STRONG>Warder's alacrity:</STRONG></SPAN></P>
<UL type=disc **SMURF**?MARGIN-TOP: 0in?>
<LI class=MsoNormal **SMURF**?MARGIN: 0in 0pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-list: level1 tab-stops: list .5in? l2 lfo3;><SPAN ?Century Gothic?? **SMURF**?mso-bidi-font-family:>Lower the cost of the AA.<SPAN **SMURF**?mso-spacerun: yes?>&nbsp; </SPAN>Right now this AA costs 45 AA for all 5 ranks.<SPAN **SMURF**?mso-spacerun: yes?>&nbsp; </SPAN>The skill should have a cost similar to warder's fury that is 3 per rank.</SPAN> 
<LI class=MsoNormal **SMURF**?MARGIN: 0in 0pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none; mso-list: level1 tab-stops: list .5in? l2 lfo3;><SPAN ?Century Gothic?? **SMURF**?mso-bidi-font-family:>Increase the DPS boost this AA gives.<SPAN **SMURF**?mso-spacerun: yes?>&nbsp; </SPAN>We are paying AA to boost one aspect of our DPS with this AA. <SPAN **SMURF**?mso-spacerun: yes?>&nbsp;</SPAN>If the AA added 10% to our pets DPS that'd still only be ~3%-5% to our total DPS.<SPAN **SMURF**?mso-spacerun: yes?>&nbsp; </SPAN>As it stands right now the boost to our pets DPS is too low and the resulting boost to our total damage is too low as well.</SPAN></LI></UL></DIV></DIV>
